{"tid":2200691,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民進黨立委：台灣政府不會怠慢苛刻5名被扣港人","createTime":"2020-09-13T07:19:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T07:43:38.000Z","uid":20933,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"901a358a51f4d0e8ee36e016eb791d56259af552","tid":2200691,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T07:19:51.000Z","msg":"台灣傳媒工作者鐘聖雄在社交網站指，7月經東沙島偷渡到台灣的5名香港示威者，已被台灣當局扣留近2個月，無法會見律師及人權團體。<br />\n<br />\n陸委會說，不會針對個別個案說明，希望外界不要作不必要揣測。民進黨立委鄭運鵬在社交網站發文說，當局不向中間人及親友透露詳情，是防弊措施，毋須被認為不信任這些港人，而是正在保護他們，相信政府機關不會怠慢苛刻香港朋友，呼籲在香港關心他們的親友放心。<br />\n<br />\n 鄭運鵬又說，對修訂港澳條例持保留態度，原因是現行的港澳條例保持模糊的行政授權，依現行的做法作專案處理，才能杜絕被大角利用假庇護、真木馬的戰術運用。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2357006\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2357006&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513RPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=2183c4f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2357006</a>"},{"pid":"f2b73d6f206b2e2d3196c95ee07d3d41578e7281","tid":2200691,"uid":286897,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T07:27:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"708ac7996e81970fb70a592361fe228d27b62446","tid":2200691,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T07:30:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f34e60c82dc29e08d84fab10f9a3233c9e63aa8","tid":2200691,"uid":605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f2b73d6f206b2e2d3196c95ee07d3d41578e7281","tid":2200691,"uid":286897,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T07:27:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T07:30:40.000Z","msg":"條友就算唔係共諜都係掛住自己拎光環搞爛件事嘅仆街冚家剷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c01d27409d96e2b2dff043ced7af790c9a69c737","tid":2200691,"uid":5094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T07:30:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"